RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT COMPONENT, FEE_RULE, (SELECT PAYMENT_TYPE_DESC FROM LBTM_FEE_COMPONENT_PYMNT_TYPE WHERE PAYMENT_TYPE = (SELECT PAYMENT_TYPE FROM LFTM_FEE_CLASS WHERE CLASS_CODE = A.COMPONENT AND MODULE = 'LB')) PAYMENT_TYPE, (SELECT FEE_BPS_RATE_APPLICABLE FROM LFTM_FEE_CLASS WHERE CLASS_CODE = A.COMPONENT AND MODULE = 'LB') FEE_BPS_RATE_APPLICABLE FROM LFTMS_PRODUCT_FEE A WHERE PRODUCT_CODE = ? AND NVL(STOP_ASSOCIATION, 'N') = 'N' AND COMPONENT NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT (COMPONENT) FROM LFTBS_CONTRACT_FEE WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = ?) UNION SELECT COMPONENT, FEE_RULE, (SELECT PAYMENT_TYPE_DESC FROM LBTM_FEE_COMPONENT_PYMNT_TYPE WHERE PAYMENT_TYPE = (SELECT PAYMENT_TYPE FROM LFTM_FEE_CLASS WHERE CLASS_CODE = B.COMPONENT AND MODULE = 'LB')) PAYMENT_TYPE, (SELECT FEE_BPS_RATE_APPLICABLE FROM LFTM_FEE_CLASS WHERE CLASS_CODE = B.COMPONENT AND MODULE = 'LB') FEE_BPS_RATE_APPLICABLE FROM LFTMS_PRODUCT_FEE B WHERE FEE_COLLECTION_MODE = 'D' AND PRODUCT_CODE = ? AND NVL(STOP_ASSOCIATION, 'N') = 'N' AND COMPONENT NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT COMPONENT FROM LFTBS_CONTRACT_FEE WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND COMPONENT_STATUS NOT IN ('L', 'V'))

SELECT FEE_COMPONENT,DESCRIPTION FROM LFTMS_FEE_DEFINITION UNION SELECT RULE,DESCRIPTION FROM LFTMS_RULE WHERE CURRENCY = '*.*' AND CURRENCY2 = '*.*' AND CUSTOMER = 'ALL' AND CUST_GROUP='ALL' AND BRANCH='ALL'

SELECT VW.CCY_CODE, CCY.CCY_NAME FROM OLVWS_PRODUCT_CURRENCIES VW, CYTMS_CCY_DEFN CCY WHERE VW.CCY_CODE = CCY.CCY_CODE AND VW.PRODUCT_CODE = ? AND CCY.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND CCY.AUTH_STAT = 'A' ORDER BY VW.CCY_CODE

SELECT a.CONTRACT_REF_NO, a.user_ref_no, a.product_code, b.product_description, a.counterparty, c.CUSTOMER_NAME1, a.branch FROM oltbs_contract a, oltms_product b, oltms_customer c WHERE a.product_code = b.product_code AND a.counterparty = c.CUSTOMER_NO AND a.BRANCH = global.current_branch AND a.module_code IN ('FC','LB') ORDER BY CONTRACT_REF_NO
select branch_code,branch_name from OLTMS_BRANCH where record_stat = 'O'

SELECT mis_code,code_desc FROM gltms_mis_code x,gltms_mis_class y WHERE x.mis_class = 'EXPCODE_T' AND x.active = 'A' AND y.mis_class = x.mis_class and mis_code not in (select mis_code from lftbs_fas91_fee_split_dtls where contract_ref_no = ? and component = ? and branch_code = ?) ORDER BY x.mis_code

select a.customer_no, a.customer_name1 from oltms_customer a, lbtbs_self_participant b where a.record_stat = 'O' and a.auth_stat = 'A' and a.customer_category = 'INVESTOR' and b.participant = a.customer_no and b.origination ='Y'
select customer_no, customer_name1 from oltms_customer where once_auth='Y'
select ac_gl_no ,ac_gl_desc from oltbs_account where ac_gl_rec_status = 'O'
SELECT mis_code,code_desc FROM gltms_mis_code x,gltms_mis_class y WHERE x.mis_class = 'EXPCODE_T' AND x.active = 'A' AND y.mis_class = x.mis_class ORDER BY x.mis_code

RAD_DATASOURCES.RELATION_WITH_PARENT: LFTBS_CONTRACT_FEE.CONTRACT_REF_NO = LFTBS_CONTRACT_FEE__SCH.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND LFTBS_CONTRACT_FEE.EVENT_SEQ_NO = LFTBS_CONTRACT_FEE__SCH.EVENT_SEQ_NO AND LFTBS_CONTRACT_FEE.COMPONENT = LFTBS_CONTRACT_FEE__SCH.COMPONENT

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT distinct A.counterparty,A.CUST_NAME FROM LBVW_AMND_FEE_SUMMARY A ORDER BY A.counterparty
